com.gmarciani.gmparser.models.parser.lr.recognition

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gmarciani.gmparser.models.parser.lr.recognition.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Item>

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Item>

    Production item model.

    An item represents both the reading state of a production and the look-ahead set with respect to the reading state.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Giacomo Marciani
    See Also:
    BigProductionGraph
